title: What's Next for Digital Currencies
description: A digital dollar may be coming soon. Daren Fonda, senior writer at Barron's and Darrell Duffie, professor from Stanford University discuss the next era in crypto-currencies and other digital tokens, from Bitcoin to the dollar.
